<h5>Meta Quest 3 (128GB)</h5>
<blockquote class="td_quote_box td_box_center"><p>The best Meta Quest 3 (128GB) Black Friday &amp; Cyber Monday 2023 sale so far is <strong><a href="https://www.newegg.com/meta-quest-quest-3-128gb-standalone/p/N82E16826910052">$500 bundled with $15 store credit for Quest games, from Newegg</a></strong>.</p></blockquote>
<p>That’s a $15 (3%) discount over what you’d normally pay ($15 worth of game credit that you&#8217;ll need to spend anyway). <em>All Quest 3 purchases also include the upcoming game Asgard&#8217;s Wrath 2 (normally $60) until January 27th, 2024</em>.</p>
<p>Or if you&#8217;re planning to buy an upgraded headstrap and case, you can get <a href="https://www.costco.com/meta-quest-3-128gb-with-asgard%e2%80%99s-wrath-2-game-bundle.product.4000216910.html">Quest 3 (128GB) for $600 from Costco along with an Elite Strap, carrying case, and $25 store credit for Quest games</a>. That&#8217;s a $65 (10%) savings over what you&#8217;d normally pay ($500 for the headset, $70 for the headstrap, $70 for the case, and $25 of game credit).</p>
<h5>Meta Quest 3 (512GB)</h5>
<blockquote class="td_quote_box td_box_center"><p>The best Meta Quest 3 (512GB) Black Friday &amp; Cyber Monday 2023 sale so far is <strong><a href="https://www.meta.com/quest/products/quest-2/">$650 bundled with $25 store credit for Quest games, from Newegg.</a></strong></p></blockquote>
